## Commercial Loan Malaysia: What to Watch Out For

Not all financing is created equal. Here's what savvy business owners look for:

### Understand the Total Cost

Don't just look at the "interest rate." Calculate the total repayment over the loan period. Some loans have low headline rates but pile on fees elsewhere.

### Match Tenure to Asset Life

If you're financing a machine that will be obsolete in 4 years, don't lock into a 7-year repayment schedule. You'll be paying for something you've already replaced.

### Check for Flexibility

Life happens. Can you make early repayments without penalty? What if you need to restructure the loan during a tough quarter?

### Read the Fine Print

Look for hidden charges: processing fees, insurance requirements, penalty clauses for late payment. At Ing Heng, we believe in no surprises—what you see is what you pay.

